HEADWORD: Charte
<hw>Charte</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Chart</er>.]</ety> <def>The constitution, or fundamental law, of the
French monarchy, as established on the restoration of Louis XVIII., in
1814.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

